title: yumeno_kizuna
body:
夢乃きずな
Character from [[Culture Japan]].

She has [[long hair|long]] [[blonde hair]] and [[blue eyes]].

h4. Profile
From http://www.dannychoo.com/en/post/26782/Kizuna+Yumeno.html
[quote]
Name: Kizuna Yumeno
Japanese Name: 夢乃きずな (ゆめのきずな)
Birthday: November 1st
Height: 162cm
3 size: B91cm W57cm H87cm
Age: 17
Blood type: B

Kizuna Yumeno is a beautiful girl who all the boys at school adore. She always scores top marks in all her classes and also excels in her after school activities.

Kizuna attends the same school as Mirai but even though they are in different classes, Mirai feels a sense of rivalry from Kizuna for some reason.
[/quote]

[quote]
Name: Chitose Shirasawa
Japanese Name: 白澤千歳 (しらさわちとせ)
Birthday: March 14th
Height: 149cm
3 size: B75cm W55cm H82cm
Age: 17
Blood type: A

A quiet and reserved girl who easily gets embarrassed when attention is directed at her. During the evening when all the other students have gone home, she can often be found sleeping in the research lab at school.

She has a strong passion for music and high fidelity equipment, and dreams of becoming a music producer. She also loves cakes and sweets. [/quote]

body:
Artist. Releases works under the circle name "Tsumi-chan Honpo". Gives reading of name as "ツミタニ ダイスケ".

In that post (dated 2009-09-01), Todoroki offers apologies and also clarifies that they did not trace any figures or patterns, but did trace some small articles and accessories. title: makaizou
body:
October 4th, 1971 - September 13th, 2009

Artist and sculptor.  Well known for his unauthorized figurine editing, specifically turning figurines into "razoku" figurines, which is a slang term for nudist ("naked tribe") in Japan -- specifically, turning otherwise clean figures into nudes.  He released two books detailing the techniques he uses to edit figurines in this manner, one posthumously via his friends.

Passed away abruptly in September 2009.  Several friends of his, working with his family, restored his website under a new domain name.  

* Home page: http://www.makaizo.com/
* Pixiv account: http://www.pixiv.net/member.php?id=11697
